    {
      "id": "1914750c-f3ba-80fb-8fcd-dec46483470c",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "CKT is argued to achieve the new State-of-te-art performance in predicting performance on ASSISTments2009 and ASSISTments 2015 datasets.\n",
